---
const sourceWatchImage = "/assets/test.png";
const sellWatchImage = "/assets/test.png";
---

<section class="flex justify-center py-12 px-5">
  <div class="flex gap-10 max-w-5xl w-full flex-col md:flex-row">
    <!-- Source a Watch -->
    <div class="flex-1 text-center">
      <a href="/contact">
        <img src={sourceWatchImage} alt="Source a Watch" class="w-full h-auto max-w-md object-cover mx-auto transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-105" />
      </a>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-5">
        <a href="/contact" class="text-gray-800 hover:underline">Source a Watch</a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
        With over 20 years of combined experience, we have sourced some of the rarest and most
        exclusive watches. Our commitment to quality and authenticity ensures you get only the best.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Sell Your Watch -->
    <div class="flex-1 text-center">
      <a href='/sellform'>
        <img src={sellWatchImage} alt="Sell Your Watch" class="w-full h-auto max-w-md object-cover mx-auto transition-transform duration-200 hover:scale-105" />
      </a>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-5">
        <a href='/sellform' class="text-gray-800 hover:underline">Sell Your Watch</a>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
        Integrity above all else, we know the watch market inside out, and our experts will keep you
        informed every step of the way. Get the best value for your luxury timepiece.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>